### 1. 회원가입
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@test.com",
  "password": "pass1234",
  "nickname": "테스터"
}

### 2. 중복 이메일 회원가입 (에러 케이스)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@test.com",
  "password": "pass1234",
  "nickname": "테스터2"
}

### 3. 비밀번호 검증 실패 (짧은 비밀번호)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test2@test.com",
  "password": "1234",
  "nickname": "테스터"
}

### 4. 로그인 → accessToken과 Set-Cookie 확인
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@test.com",
  "password": "pass1234"
}

### 5. 토큰 없이 로그아웃 (401/403 기대)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/logout

### 6. 로그아웃 (로그인 응답의 accessToken을 붙여넣기)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzUxMiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIyIiwiZW1haWwiOiJ0ZXN0QHRlc3QuY29tIiwicm9sZSI6IlVTRVIiLCJpYXQiOjE3NzU1NDI0MTYsImV4cCI6MTc3NTU0NDIxNn0.2MAx2pysX2EN7AKQmfU1JiNBpjBflI1JO_pISPh-9492HjmHm8NYBAd8sF9s59sKrY-BetuZaW5mOXXVamMAnw

### 7. 토큰 갱신 (로그인 응답의 Set-Cookie 값을 붙여넣기)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/refresh
Cookie: refresh_token=eyJhbGciOiJIUzUxMiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIyIiwiaWF0IjoxNzc1NTQyNDgwLCJleHAiOjE3NzYxNDcyODB9.rhI77NBhcEDwqIUI1KFbuiJ08G-bsk_tDoA38L-D5p6021zo3CmLSVljxKCCY9-MXZDbgL0p0m4fo-tAs8QAVQ
